===Noun===
'''slant'''
#A [[slope]] or [[incline]].  
#:''The house was built on a bit of a '''slant''' and was never quite level.''
#A [[bias]], [[tendency]], or [[leaning]]; a [[perspective]] or [[angle]].
#:''It was a well written article, but it had a bit of a leftist '''slant'''.''

